1
00:00:00,950 --> 00:00:03,800
Hey, all you viewers out there!

2
00:00:03,800 --> 00:00:07,120
When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make sure to keep the room nice and bright,

3
00:00:07,120 --> 00:00:09,290
and sit back from the screen, 'kay?

4
00:00:10,800 --> 00:00:12,950
Previously on Fairy Tail!

5
00:00:13,220 --> 00:00:16,490
We managed to defeat Phantom's Element 4 somehow

6
00:00:16,490 --> 00:00:20,540
which stopped the Magic Giant, but Master Jose has come to attack!

7
00:00:20,840 --> 00:00:24,090
Natsu came running to save the captured Lucy,

8
00:00:24,090 --> 00:00:28,560
and started an all-out battle with the Iron Dragon Slayer, Gajeel!

9
00:00:49,220 --> 00:00:53,630
It'll be all right! I'll yell it out countless times.

10
00:00:53,630 --> 00:00:58,700
I believe your every tomorrow will be shining.

11
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:01,050
The intersection of all people

12
00:01:01,050 --> 00:01:03,660
whose dreams have come true is one point:

13
00:01:03,660 --> 00:01:08,290
Never giving up.  And that's why we're not gonna lose!

14
00:01:08,290 --> 00:01:13,470
When it seems like you'll be blown away by the headwinds,

15
00:01:13,470 --> 00:01:15,620
grasp this hand, try to take a chance.

16
00:01:15,620 --> 00:01:18,890
Because you're not alone anymore, got it?

17
00:01:22,010 --> 00:01:24,000
Go forward, more and more!

18
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:26,520
Don't give up on your awesome dream!

19
00:01:26,520 --> 00:01:27,780
That's right, don't cry!

20
00:01:27,780 --> 00:01:29,250
Move on, my way!

21
00:01:29,250 --> 00:01:31,630
Now, with the light shining down upon you.

22
00:01:31,630 --> 00:01:33,710
Don't even think about something like giving up!

23
00:01:33,710 --> 00:01:36,140
Even if you trade being hurt again for strength.

24
00:01:36,140 --> 00:01:41,630
Your eyes, always looking straight ahead,

25
00:01:41,630 --> 00:01:45,910
can surely see the light!

26
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:08,670
It's so easy to lure you out, Salamader.

27
00:02:08,670 --> 00:02:12,520
That's 'cause you keep playing dirty, Iron Dragon!

28
00:02:14,370 --> 00:02:15,390
Natsu!

29
00:02:17,570 --> 00:02:19,740
Lucy, get back.

30
00:02:19,740 --> 00:02:21,030
Gajeel!

31
00:02:21,030 --> 00:02:22,530
Stay outta this!

32
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:24,530
Bring it!

33
00:02:30,820 --> 00:02:33,000
Keep us outta this!

34
00:02:42,300 --> 00:02:46,060
Talons of the Fire Dragon!

35
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:50,710
Lucy, are you okay?

36
00:02:50,710 --> 00:02:51,850
Happy!

37
00:02:53,100 --> 00:02:54,520
What's the matter?

38
00:02:55,750 --> 00:02:56,900
Yeah...

39
00:02:58,450 --> 00:03:01,300
I've never seen Natsu like that.

40
00:03:01,300 --> 00:03:03,900
Aye. Neither have I.

41
00:03:03,900 --> 00:03:07,050
But Natsu is really powerful right now.

42
00:03:11,210 --> 00:03:13,830
The Two Dragon Slayers!

43
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:18,780
You're sure actin' uppity, trash.

44
00:03:18,780 --> 00:03:23,160
Same to you! You beat Lucy up...

45
00:03:23,160 --> 00:03:26,400
So I'm gonna bend that face of yours and turn it into iron filings.

46
00:03:27,270 --> 00:03:30,180
Sounds like fun. Try me!

47
00:03:41,880 --> 00:03:43,610
What's that dangerous looking thing?

48
00:03:44,310 --> 00:03:46,180
Sword of the Iron Dragon.

49
00:03:46,180 --> 00:03:49,670
There's nothing that won't be cut to sheds when hit with this!

50
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:53,980
I want to test how well this cuts on you, Salamander!

51
00:03:53,980 --> 00:03:55,790
That ain't nothing!

52
00:03:56,090 --> 00:03:57,710
What's that?

53
00:03:57,710 --> 00:03:59,630
It's Iron Dragon Slayer Magic!

54
00:04:01,590 --> 00:04:04,090
We're caught up in it again!

55
00:04:05,590 --> 00:04:09,640
Can't stop it now like you did before, huh?

56
00:04:09,640 --> 00:04:11,640
I thought you said it ain't nothing!

57
00:04:15,110 --> 00:04:17,600
You actually move pretty well there.

58
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:19,320
Same to you.

59
00:04:19,700 --> 00:04:22,810
That last time was just the preliminaries, after all.

60
00:04:22,810 --> 00:04:25,160
Let's finish this, Salamander!

61
00:04:26,210 --> 00:04:29,120
Now I'm fired up, you scrap-iron bastard!

62
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:36,100
Both of them are Dragon Slayers who can transform their bodies to take on characteristics of dragons!

63
00:04:36,100 --> 00:04:40,590
For two human Dragon Slayer wizards to battle...

64
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:43,740
What's going to happen?

65
00:04:48,840 --> 00:04:50,900
I will destroy you!

66
00:04:50,900 --> 00:04:51,730
His body!

67
00:04:51,730 --> 00:04:53,200
Scales of the Dragon!

68
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:57,480
Hard Fist of the Iron Dragon!

69
00:04:59,810 --> 00:05:01,090
We're caught up in it a third time!

70
00:05:01,090 --> 00:05:02,280
I've had enough!

71
00:05:04,820 --> 00:05:07,810
That made a nice sound.

72
00:05:10,670 --> 00:05:13,450
Natsu was bruised with just one hit?

73
00:05:13,450 --> 00:05:16,080
Those scales are made of the hardest steel.

74
00:05:23,840 --> 00:05:26,760
No way! That's the air pressure from his kick?

75
00:05:26,760 --> 00:05:30,180
Those steel scales have doubled the strength of his attacks!

76
00:05:34,160 --> 00:05:38,380
These steel scales render all your attacks powerless!

77
00:05:40,950 --> 00:05:43,390
Oh, no! His defense is upped?

78
00:05:43,390 --> 00:05:44,440
Natsu!

79
00:05:47,050 --> 00:05:48,200
It doesn't hurt!

80
00:05:48,200 --> 00:05:51,150
It doesn't hurt, damn it!

81
00:05:51,150 --> 00:05:52,510
...he says.

82
00:05:52,510 --> 00:05:53,700
Aye.

83
00:05:54,060 --> 00:05:56,120
Shut up already!

84
00:05:56,400 --> 00:06:00,300
That's enough pretending you're okay!

85
00:06:01,770 --> 00:06:03,740
You clanky bastard!

86
00:06:03,740 --> 00:06:05,410
I'll blow you away!

87
00:06:05,410 --> 00:06:06,760
Roar of the...

88
00:06:06,760 --> 00:06:08,870
Roar of the...

89
00:06:09,840 --> 00:06:11,930
He can use a breath attack,too!

90
00:06:12,760 --> 00:06:15,000
...Fire Dragon!

91
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:17,590
...Iron Dragon!

92
00:06:26,190 --> 00:06:28,300
That's the 4th time we're caught up in it.

93
00:06:28,300 --> 00:06:29,840
That's our Gajeel...

94
00:06:29,840 --> 00:06:34,530
It looks like the difference in the two dragons is obvious now, Salamander.

95
00:06:35,750 --> 00:06:39,640
Even if your flaming breath can wipe out enemies,

96
00:06:39,640 --> 00:06:42,830
against steal it doesn't even make a scratch.

97
00:06:42,830 --> 00:06:49,340
But my breath of iron blades has torn your body to shreds.

98
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:50,990
Natsu...

99
00:06:50,990 --> 00:06:53,300
He's... strong!

100
00:06:54,330 --> 00:06:58,480
Not a scratch, you say? Sure you're not a bit groggy?

101
00:06:59,890 --> 00:07:01,480
It cracked!

102
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:04,720
My flames are not just any fire!

103
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:08,090
The flames of the Fire Dragon destroy everything!

104
00:07:10,180 --> 00:07:14,320
If you don't get serious, I'll crush you to pieces, Gajeel the Iron Dragon!

105
00:07:14,320 --> 00:07:16,370
Enough feeling each other out!

106
00:07:17,570 --> 00:07:20,370
Sounds good to me!

107
00:07:21,860 --> 00:07:23,380
Feeling each other out?

108
00:07:23,380 --> 00:07:25,640
Neither of them were being serious?

109
00:07:25,640 --> 00:07:27,140
They're monsters!

110
00:07:27,140 --> 00:07:29,250
They're Dragon Slayers!

111
00:07:29,250 --> 00:07:33,340
Incredible... And wait, why did they strip?

112
00:07:33,340 --> 00:07:36,220
Come 'ere, Gajeel the Iron Dragon!

113
00:07:36,220 --> 00:07:39,720
There's not enough room in the sky for two dragons!

114
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:43,560
I'll drop you, Natsu the Salamander!

115
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:47,070
Natsu...

116
00:07:57,490 --> 00:08:00,180
Hey, wait... What's with the creepy hand movement?

117
00:08:00,180 --> 00:08:01,650
<i>That's</i> what you're worried about?

118
00:08:01,650 --> 00:08:02,960
This doesn't look good.

119
00:08:10,260 --> 00:08:13,250
Our Guild! What are you doing?!

120
00:08:13,250 --> 00:08:15,340
Shoot it down!

121
00:08:24,890 --> 00:08:26,400
What's with those two?

122
00:08:26,400 --> 00:08:27,520
They jumped!

123
00:08:36,470 --> 00:08:37,780
The heck?

124
00:08:38,550 --> 00:08:39,780
Light?

125
00:08:45,500 --> 00:08:47,430
W-Whoa...

126
00:08:47,430 --> 00:08:49,160
He's keeping up with Gajeel like that!

127
00:08:49,160 --> 00:08:50,440
I can't believe it!

128
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:01,970
Now <i>we're</i> getting caught up in it!

129
00:09:06,390 --> 00:09:08,280
Gajeel's getting beaten down!

130
00:09:08,280 --> 00:09:12,210
No, but look! Salamander's also outta breath!

131
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:19,050
That's <i>so</i> not fair!

132
00:09:19,050 --> 00:09:20,240
Don't eat by yourself!

133
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:21,380
Shubab!

134
00:09:21,380 --> 00:09:23,550
He really does eat iron...

135
00:09:23,550 --> 00:09:24,950
Does it taste good?

136
00:09:26,190 --> 00:09:28,170
Now that I've eaten, I'm all revved up!

137
00:09:28,410 --> 00:09:29,920
Don't copy me!

138
00:09:31,550 --> 00:09:34,850
What? He's suddenly full of energy!

139
00:09:34,850 --> 00:09:41,850
Dragon Slayers can restore their energy and power up by eating their respective element!

140
00:09:42,150 --> 00:09:44,190
Then Natsu needs to eat fire!

141
00:09:45,050 --> 00:09:46,310
That's right...

142
00:09:46,310 --> 00:09:51,120
Natsu can't eat his own magic flames!

143
00:09:51,120 --> 00:09:53,690
But... What should he do?

144
00:09:53,690 --> 00:09:55,880
I'll tear you to shreds!

145
00:09:55,880 --> 00:09:57,530
Spears of the Iron Dragon!

146
00:09:57,530 --> 00:09:59,080
Demon Poles!

147
00:10:02,380 --> 00:10:06,000
Fire, fire... Did I have a fire Spirit?

148
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:10,900
Oh yeah... I lost my keys.

149
00:10:13,770 --> 00:10:18,390
The only one I have on hand is the new one, Sagittarius.

150
00:10:19,610 --> 00:10:21,640
I haven't made a contract yet, but...

151
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:27,020
But this is the only chance we've got!

152
00:10:39,950 --> 00:10:42,530
Stop!!

153
00:10:42,530 --> 00:10:43,260
Cana!

154
00:10:42,530 --> 00:10:45,430
Our guild is being...

155
00:10:49,380 --> 00:10:52,460
I am linked to the path to the world of Celestial Spirits!

156
00:10:52,460 --> 00:10:55,880
Now! O Spirit, answer my call and pass through the Gate!

157
00:10:58,260 --> 00:11:01,550
Gate of the Archer, I open thee!

158
00:11:02,220 --> 00:11:04,270
Sagittarius!

159
00:11:09,750 --> 00:11:11,640
Horse!

160
00:11:12,800 --> 00:11:14,750
I am here! Moshimoshi.

161
00:11:14,750 --> 00:11:16,570
Look, he's here!

162
00:11:16,570 --> 00:11:19,000
And wearing a horse-suit!

163
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:20,550
I'll explain the details later!

164
00:11:20,550 --> 00:11:22,020
Can you shoot fire?

165
00:11:20,620 --> 00:11:22,020
Horsemeat...

166
00:11:22,020 --> 00:11:24,710
No. For I am an archer, as it were!

167
00:11:24,710 --> 00:11:25,950
Moshimoshi!

168
00:11:25,950 --> 00:11:27,760
R-Right...

169
00:11:27,760 --> 00:11:29,790
Where are you saluting to?

170
00:11:30,510 --> 00:11:33,030
Lucy! It's dangerous, so get back!

171
00:11:33,030 --> 00:11:34,190
A-Aye!

172
00:11:34,190 --> 00:11:34,960
Moshimoshi!

173
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:41,800
Getting Down on Yourself Time

174
00:11:35,260 --> 00:11:38,290
I'm so useless!

175
00:11:38,290 --> 00:11:39,990
Now now, look on the bright side.

176
00:11:39,990 --> 00:11:42,340
As it were!

177
00:11:42,340 --> 00:11:43,720
Here I go!

178
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:47,760
Edge of the Fire Dragon!

179
00:11:48,440 --> 00:11:51,140
Don't have any power on an empty stomach?

180
00:11:52,980 --> 00:11:55,480
Then eat some iron!

181
00:11:59,770 --> 00:12:01,560
I knew it... Gajeel is...

182
00:12:01,560 --> 00:12:03,320
...way stronger!

183
00:12:03,880 --> 00:12:06,070
I've got no more use for you.

184
00:12:08,060 --> 00:12:09,990
Disappear, trash!

185
00:12:11,340 --> 00:12:13,000
Oh, no!

186
00:12:18,340 --> 00:12:21,530
I don't want that!

187
00:12:21,530 --> 00:12:25,300
I couldn't stand Natsu losing!

188
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:32,070
Take a look at what's happening to what you're trying to protect!

189
00:12:53,510 --> 00:12:58,190
It's huge! Is this a wizard's guild?

190
00:12:58,190 --> 00:13:00,030
Fairy Tail!

191
00:13:00,030 --> 00:13:02,170
Fairy Tail?

192
00:13:02,960 --> 00:13:07,260
Yes. Do Fairies have tails?

193
00:13:07,260 --> 00:13:11,830
Nobody even knows if they exist in the first place.

194
00:13:11,830 --> 00:13:14,300
That's why it's an eternal mystery.

195
00:13:14,300 --> 00:13:16,310
An eternal adventure.

196
00:13:16,530 --> 00:13:19,750
That's the meaning behind the name.

197
00:13:19,750 --> 00:13:22,360
I don't really get it, but awesome!

198
00:13:25,610 --> 00:13:29,010
What's your problem? I don't like your look.

199
00:13:29,560 --> 00:13:30,950
Oh, picking a fight?

200
00:13:30,950 --> 00:13:32,100
Do it! Do it!

201
00:13:32,100 --> 00:13:33,820
Gray, your clothes!

202
00:13:33,820 --> 00:13:36,160
Oh, you're just a freak!

203
00:13:36,600 --> 00:13:38,400
Who're you callin' a freak, squinty eyes!

204
00:13:38,400 --> 00:13:41,150
I'm talkin' about you, droopy eyes!

205
00:13:41,150 --> 00:13:43,360
Nice and spirited, they are.

206
00:13:43,360 --> 00:13:44,960
That's how it should be.

207
00:13:50,680 --> 00:13:51,770
Enough!

208
00:13:51,770 --> 00:13:53,350
You think I'm gonna quit?

209
00:13:53,350 --> 00:13:54,230
That idiot!

210
00:13:55,630 --> 00:13:57,190
Fools...

211
00:13:58,080 --> 00:13:59,860
Why me, too?

212
00:13:59,860 --> 00:14:01,620
No fighting!

213
00:14:01,620 --> 00:14:02,200
Got it?

214
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:03,680
R-Right!

215
00:14:03,680 --> 00:14:06,440
S-Strong... S-Scary...

216
00:14:06,440 --> 00:14:08,270
What's your name?

217
00:14:09,430 --> 00:14:10,730
Natsu.

218
00:14:10,730 --> 00:14:12,660
Natsu, huh?

219
00:14:12,660 --> 00:14:13,760
Listen.

220
00:14:13,760 --> 00:14:16,730
Everyone who comes to Fairy Tail are like family.

221
00:14:16,730 --> 00:14:18,750
And this is our house.

222
00:14:18,750 --> 00:14:20,810
A family's house is not a place to fight.

223
00:14:20,810 --> 00:14:21,920
Do you understand?

224
00:14:25,260 --> 00:14:27,050
I am Erza.

225
00:14:27,050 --> 00:14:27,840
Nice to meet you.

226
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:30,190
Erza's scary...

227
00:14:30,190 --> 00:14:31,920
See?

228
00:14:41,130 --> 00:14:43,710
Natsu, where are you going?

229
00:14:43,710 --> 00:14:44,900
Hey you, isn't that...

230
00:14:45,850 --> 00:14:48,280
I'm gonna go do this job!

231
00:14:48,280 --> 00:14:51,390
You <i>do</i> understand what that request says, right?

232
00:14:51,770 --> 00:14:52,870
Um...

233
00:14:53,220 --> 00:14:55,610
Need something-something exterminated...

234
00:14:55,610 --> 00:14:59,010
Something is something at something, maybe?

235
00:14:59,010 --> 00:15:00,830
The reward is 50,000 jewel!

236
00:15:00,830 --> 00:15:02,390
You didn't read it at all!

237
00:15:02,390 --> 00:15:03,600
Shut up!

238
00:15:03,600 --> 00:15:08,070
You can't even read. All you understood was the reward, idiot.

239
00:15:08,070 --> 00:15:09,210
Mira-nee!

240
00:15:10,490 --> 00:15:12,210
I can read!

241
00:15:12,210 --> 00:15:15,770
Igneel taught me the letters!

242
00:15:15,770 --> 00:15:19,730
I just don't get what's written here!

243
00:15:20,030 --> 00:15:21,140
Natsu!

244
00:15:21,140 --> 00:15:24,010
I remember all the names of food!

245
00:15:24,010 --> 00:15:25,020
Hamburger!

246
00:15:25,020 --> 00:15:25,910
Spaghetti!

247
00:15:25,910 --> 00:15:26,760
Rice-bowls!

248
00:15:26,760 --> 00:15:28,100
Cakes and cookies!

249
00:15:28,100 --> 00:15:29,420
Stew, soup!

250
00:15:29,420 --> 00:15:30,960
And...

251
00:15:30,960 --> 00:15:35,630
Damn it! Well excuse me for only knowing names of food!

252
00:15:35,630 --> 00:15:36,580
But...

253
00:15:36,580 --> 00:15:39,120
He really taught me!

254
00:15:39,120 --> 00:15:44,040
Igneel really taught me the letters...

255
00:15:44,040 --> 00:15:47,170
Creepy

256
00:15:44,340 --> 00:15:47,170
Don't cry, Natsu... So cute...

257
00:15:47,170 --> 00:15:48,970
Hey, you! Hands off!

258
00:15:48,970 --> 00:15:50,260
I'm not crying!

259
00:15:50,260 --> 00:15:52,840
That's enough, you three.

260
00:15:53,230 --> 00:15:54,570
Erza...

261
00:15:54,570 --> 00:15:56,580
It's nothing to be embarrassed about.

262
00:15:56,580 --> 00:15:58,680
Nor is it Igneel's fault.

263
00:15:58,680 --> 00:16:01,910
In this world there are an endless number of words, after all.

264
00:16:01,910 --> 00:16:03,060
Oh, be quiet.

265
00:16:03,360 --> 00:16:05,910
If you don't know them, then you should learn them, that's all.

266
00:16:05,910 --> 00:16:07,800
Come! I will teach you.

267
00:16:07,800 --> 00:16:09,070
No way!

268
00:16:09,070 --> 00:16:11,850
You're scary! No way!

269
00:16:11,850 --> 00:16:13,640
I'm just going to teach you some vocabulary...

270
00:16:13,640 --> 00:16:14,960
What's scary about that?

271
00:16:14,960 --> 00:16:16,450
No, no!

272
00:16:19,890 --> 00:16:22,330
Natsu, hang in there! Seriously...

273
00:16:22,630 --> 00:16:25,070
Serves him right, the half-wit.

274
00:16:25,620 --> 00:16:28,390
Oh, yeah? Underpants Shogun!

275
00:16:28,390 --> 00:16:30,190
You wanna go, General Snot?

276
00:16:30,190 --> 00:16:31,820
No playing around!

277
00:16:31,820 --> 00:16:32,980
Three days!

278
00:16:32,980 --> 00:16:33,590
Yes?

279
00:16:34,320 --> 00:16:37,150
Think of me as Igneel the 2nd.

280
00:16:37,150 --> 00:16:42,590
I will pound into you all the necessary vocabulary to live as a Fairy Tail wizard in three days!

281
00:16:42,890 --> 00:16:46,300
Until that time I will not allow you to eat, drink, or sleep!

282
00:16:47,900 --> 00:16:52,170
Then, yeah! I'm gonna do this thing!

283
00:16:53,040 --> 00:16:56,190
So, do you like the guild, Natsu?

284
00:16:56,610 --> 00:17:01,630
Yeah, I do! Erza's scary, but other than that, it's all super fun!

285
00:17:01,630 --> 00:17:04,170
And I remember lots and lots of words!

286
00:17:04,170 --> 00:17:06,330
I want to join here!

287
00:17:06,330 --> 00:17:09,000
It's an egg! I found an egg!

288
00:17:09,300 --> 00:17:11,630
When we grow up...

289
00:17:12,310 --> 00:17:14,920
...can I be your wife?

290
00:17:15,800 --> 00:17:18,490
What are you talkin' about all of a sudden?

291
00:17:19,590 --> 00:17:21,370
How pretty...

292
00:17:22,220 --> 00:17:25,810
I wish this instant would last forever...

293
00:17:28,320 --> 00:17:29,190
A cat?!

294
00:17:29,520 --> 00:17:31,430
How cute!

295
00:17:31,430 --> 00:17:34,070
He's like a bluebird of happiness!

296
00:17:34,300 --> 00:17:35,770
Happiness, huh?

297
00:17:35,770 --> 00:17:38,830
Then I'll name him Happy!

298
00:17:38,830 --> 00:17:39,620
Aye!

299
00:17:41,050 --> 00:17:43,580
An S-class? No fair, man!

300
00:17:44,250 --> 00:17:46,260
Don't be jealous.

301
00:17:46,260 --> 00:17:49,170
You'll be able to do S-class's yourself before you know it, Natsu.

302
00:17:49,170 --> 00:17:50,460
And when's that?

303
00:17:50,760 --> 00:17:55,080
Well, I don't know. But when you do, I'll support you.

304
00:17:55,080 --> 00:17:58,840
Until that time, you do your best to protect Fairy Tail, okay?

305
00:17:58,840 --> 00:18:01,110
Lisanna, hurry up!

306
00:17:59,910 --> 00:18:02,330
Bring us back a souvenir!

307
00:18:02,340 --> 00:18:03,970
Natsu!

308
00:18:07,210 --> 00:18:09,230
I'm heading off!

309
00:18:15,610 --> 00:18:17,450
So long...

310
00:18:21,940 --> 00:18:23,950
I'm Lucy. Nice to meet you!

311
00:18:24,200 --> 00:18:26,920
I know I don't seem like it, but I'm actually a wizard myself!

312
00:18:26,920 --> 00:18:31,580
The one I want to get into, see, has like a ton of amazing wizards, and....

313
00:18:31,580 --> 00:18:33,790
It's called Fairy Tail!

314
00:18:34,090 --> 00:18:37,660
Then come with me to our guild!

315
00:18:38,260 --> 00:18:42,760
One cannot progress in the way of magic by being mindful of the watchful eye from above!

316
00:18:42,760 --> 00:18:45,800
Follow the path you believe in!

317
00:18:45,800 --> 00:18:49,690
That's what it means to be a Fairy Tail wizard!

318
00:18:55,200 --> 00:18:56,480
My magical power...

319
00:18:56,480 --> 00:18:57,650
Master!

320
00:18:57,950 --> 00:19:00,990
But, I still want to be in the guild...

321
00:19:02,250 --> 00:19:05,580
I love Fairy Tail!

322
00:19:10,180 --> 00:19:11,290
Natsu...

323
00:19:12,920 --> 00:19:14,780
Enough, Natsu...

324
00:19:14,780 --> 00:19:20,980
If... If they have me, then...

325
00:19:20,980 --> 00:19:22,360
Lucy...

326
00:19:24,040 --> 00:19:27,260
Natsu hasn't given up yet.

327
00:19:31,850 --> 00:19:36,480
Your guild has fallen. You lose!

328
00:19:43,160 --> 00:19:46,100
But, any more of this, and I...

329
00:19:47,550 --> 00:19:50,790
Stay down already, Salamander.

330
00:19:50,790 --> 00:19:54,130
I really hate holding back, you see...

331
00:19:54,130 --> 00:19:56,250
I don't know what might happen to you.

332
00:19:56,250 --> 00:20:00,670
Destroying Jupiter, battling fiercely with the Element 4...

333
00:20:00,670 --> 00:20:03,220
He used up too much magic power!

334
00:20:03,220 --> 00:20:07,870
If only he could eat some flames, Natsu wouldn't lose to anybody!

335
00:20:07,870 --> 00:20:09,430
So they say...

336
00:20:09,430 --> 00:20:11,590
Too bad for you.

337
00:20:11,890 --> 00:20:13,350
I see.

338
00:20:13,350 --> 00:20:17,830
It seems I had a slight misunderstanding, as it were. Moshimoshi.

339
00:20:17,830 --> 00:20:23,860
You inquired whether I could shoot fire, Madame Lucy, and I replied, "No."

340
00:20:23,860 --> 00:20:30,400
However what is crucial at this point is not shooting fire, but the fire itself, am I right?

341
00:20:30,400 --> 00:20:30,950
Moshimoshi.

342
00:20:31,830 --> 00:20:34,840
The final blow, Salamander!

343
00:20:43,050 --> 00:20:44,580
Fire!

344
00:20:44,580 --> 00:20:47,240
Flames from causing the machines to explode!

345
00:20:47,240 --> 00:20:52,920
Depending on how one shoots, it is possible to pierce through or shatter, as it were.

346
00:20:52,920 --> 00:20:54,020
Moshimoshi.

347
00:20:54,020 --> 00:20:56,850
What the hell is that horse-ish thing?

348
00:20:57,120 --> 00:21:00,570
Wow! You're like a genius archer, Sagittarius!

349
00:21:00,570 --> 00:21:02,560
Correct, moshimoshi.

350
00:21:02,560 --> 00:21:04,740
But where are you saluting too?

351
00:21:11,940 --> 00:21:13,880
That hit the spot.

352
00:21:14,470 --> 00:21:16,540
Thanks, Lucy!

353
00:21:18,580 --> 00:21:22,730
Don't get all full of yourself just cause you ate some fire!

354
00:21:25,010 --> 00:21:25,960
All right!

355
00:21:25,960 --> 00:21:28,340
Now he's at full power!

356
00:21:31,200 --> 00:21:32,970
This isn't good! No way!

357
00:21:32,970 --> 00:21:40,020
Levy, Jet, Droy, Gramps, Lucy, my friends...

358
00:21:40,020 --> 00:21:42,900
And Fairy Tail...

359
00:21:42,900 --> 00:21:46,490
Roar of the Iron Dragon!

360
00:21:50,120 --> 00:21:53,830
He deflected my breath with just his bare hands?

361
00:21:55,420 --> 00:22:00,890
How much do you gotta hurt others before you people are satisfied?

362
00:22:01,130 --> 00:22:02,730
Impossible!

363
00:22:02,730 --> 00:22:04,190
I couldn't...

364
00:22:04,190 --> 00:22:05,380
To someone like him...

365
00:22:05,710 --> 00:22:07,470
To trash like him...

366
00:22:07,470 --> 00:22:10,820
I'm going to pay you back for everything!

367
00:22:10,820 --> 00:22:14,970
I'll show you that picking a fight with Fairy Tail was a mistake!

368
00:22:18,220 --> 00:22:20,400
To be continued!

369
00:22:20,400 --> 00:22:22,160
Is that really still necessary?!

370
00:22:22,160 --> 00:22:24,980
As it were! Moshimoshi.

371
00:23:56,430 --> 00:24:01,720
Oh yeah... What ever happened to our punishment from going on that S-class quest without permission?

372
00:24:01,720 --> 00:24:04,100
Hey, don't remind people of that!

373
00:24:04,100 --> 00:24:06,810
But we have to prepare ourselves, or...

374
00:24:06,810 --> 00:24:11,360
Why don't we get them to change the rule about not going on S-class quests?

375
00:24:11,360 --> 00:24:14,460
Sure... You go talk to the master about that, Natsu.

376
00:24:14,460 --> 00:24:16,550
Next time: Fairy Law!

377
00:24:16,820 --> 00:24:19,090
Oh, yeah... I'm kinda busy today...

378
00:24:19,090 --> 00:24:20,390
Natsu, are you running away?

379
00:24:20,390 --> 00:24:23,390
Me, run away?! I'm just, um, heading out for a bit...

380
00:24:23,390 --> 00:24:24,560
Just a bit!

